(1, 1, 'Conana tủtorial', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://salt.tikicdn.com/ts/tmp/8c/62/1d/175a40345e370bef182b4da130512b4f.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Test your detective skills and uncover the secret:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is a war of detectives and dangerous criminals so there is no room for baseless arguments. Remember that no matter which side you are on, only inference will bring the truth and solve the secrets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://salt.tikicdn.com/ts/tmp/0a/c1/c1/07e87ed75cc370515cee5274597d0244.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Especially referring to Conan, it is impossible not to mention Doctor Agasha and his wonderful inventions.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Those wonderful inventions have turned into valuable treasures to help our Little Detective&#39;s faction to investigate and expose the Black Organization. Feel it for yourself and see how Conan&#39;s familiar discoveries will help you investigate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://salt.tikicdn.com/ts/tmp/89/0a/aa/173b160f2dcd211fa5630af4d96c1e86.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Exclusive gift for fans: The famous Detective Conan character profile is very beautiful:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the first time, the characters of the comic series &quot;Famous Detective Conan&quot; appear together in a set of &quot;very Conan&quot; character profiles with impeccable quality: glossy colored paper, character information The standard does not need to be adjusted and especially the sayings that make up the name of the character in the game.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://salt.tikicdn.com/ts/tmp/aa/db/f9/0baa28ae065ff0967f3761ffac287dbc.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>You are ready to enter the world of &quot;Famous Detective Conan: The End&quot; and create your own &quot;end&quot;.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product prices on Tiki include tax according to applicable law. However, depending on the type of product or the method and delivery address, there may be additional costs such as shipping fees, surcharges for bulky goods, ...</p>', 1, '2021-07-10 09:14:22', '2021-10-27 08:09:00'),
(2, 2, 'Bee Smart	', '<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>The composition of each game set includes:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;62 playing cards, each card has 6 pictures corresponding to 6 words.<br />\r\n&nbsp;1 sheet of name reading corresponds to 62 words, in both English and Vietnamese.<br />\r\n&nbsp;1 instruction sheet, with 3 basic gameplay can be applied immediately.<br />\r\nThere are many ways to play from these cards, all based on rules:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Between any 2 cards, there is always 1 and only 1 common image.<br />\r\nThe winner is the one who finds the pattern the fastest and reads it out loud.<br />\r\nThe game is available in both English and Vietnamese, but it is recommended to use English when playing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The game will be more attractive when played in large numbers and there are rewards for the winners. However, for preschool children, parents can play with their children to encourage them to play and use English.</p>', 1, '2021-07-10 23:57:30', '2021-10-28 07:56:22'),
(3, 5, 'Difference', '<p>To start, each player looks at the top card of her stack, then tries to spot the two differences between her card in hand and the reference card on the table. Whoever spots her particular differences first stops play, demonstrates them to everyone, places her card on top of the reference card (creating a new challenge for everyone), then draws the next card from her deck. Whoever gets rid of all of her cards first wins!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"inside the box\" src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Puz8xkKfHNl1mx73hih6PA__imagepage/img/rYqZY1GRMExuTly-_Sf9Kr4_1pI=/fit-in/900x600/filters:no_upscale():strip_icc()/pic829048.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"game in process\" src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/woWVXeYE1dPgkQACJqKOSg__imagepage/img/_uE4UFLfmXHhw99itA5ixfNpmy0=/fit-in/900x600/filters:no_upscale():strip_icc()/pic829049.jpg\" /></p>', 1, '2021-07-11 00:08:25', '2021-10-28 08:14:41'),
(4, 6, 'dragomino-1	', '<p>Dragomino is Kingdomino&#39;s version of dragon seeker<br />\r\nYou will play as a dragon trainer who sets out to find a rare baby dragon, but hurry up because you are not the only trainer.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nYou will have to compete with other trainers too</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"#Boardgameshot\" src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CznKfvsPrSs5NTdEB63ZrA__imagepage/img/dNgJwgJ_9gViKAWZzuZcDBG44wA=/fit-in/900x600/filters:no_upscale():strip_icc()/pic6107328.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"#Boardgameshot\" src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/gdjnAwIEKx55hYUiHlz2HA__imagepage/img/73776B5ETcUx2VHr6On7mDJHeIY=/fit-in/900x600/filters:no_upscale():strip_icc()/pic6107327.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"#Boardgameshot\" src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/31cVJJUxIga7Cwy88YjA7A__imagepage/img/oOHLm1COi_-2IJOuWsioem9Jy7Q=/fit-in/900x600/filters:no_upscale():strip_icc()/pic6107326.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"#Boardgameshot\" src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/KwF7S3nWeffGIDhadJn16A__imagepage/img/HsipxdCdMQGkIcaehKMYN7twwn0=/fit-in/900x600/filters:no_upscale():strip_icc()/pic6107323.jpg\" /></p>', 1, '2021-07-11 07:03:59', '2021-10-28 08:18:34'),
(7, 7, 'New York Slice	', '<p>In&nbsp;<em><strong>New York Slice</strong></em>, each player slices pizzas into portions, giving their opponents first choice, while they take the leftovers. There are a dozen kinds of pizza to work with, from veggie to hawaiian to meat lover&#39;s, and each player decides if they want to eat or keep some of the slices, building the best collection of pizzas possible!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each time a player slices a pizza, there&#39;s a different special to go along with it, whether it&#39;s allocated to one of the portions or placed on its own. Specials provide the player with special powers or points, such as calling dibs on a slice before the pizza is divided, getting one of the normally-out-of-the-game &quot;mystery slices&#39;, having an opportunity to &quot;sneak a slice&quot; by moving it from one portion to another when they choose, and many more&mdash;there are 14 different &quot;Today&#39;s Specials&quot; in the game.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some slices have anchovies on them (yuck!), which are worth negative points to anyone who collects them &mdash; but anchovies might show up on different pizza types you&#39;re collecting, so in order to have the majority of a type, you just might have to collect one with anchovies on it!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you tie another player for the most slices of a type, neither of you gets any points &mdash; but a bunch of slices have two types of pizza on them, with each combo slice being worth half a slice of each type, which is great for breaking ties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most slices have pepperoni on them, which you can eat for points (instead of collecting to go for the majority of each slice type).</p>', 1, '2021-07-11 08:43:15', '2021-10-28 08:05:33'),
(8, 8, 'Splendor', '<p><img alt=\"Splendor boardgame\" src=\"https://cdn-www.bluestacks.com/bs-images/banner5_013.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>On your turn, you may (1) collect chips (gems), or (2) buy and build a card, or (3) reserve one card. If you collect chips, you take either three different kinds of chips or two chips of the same kind. If you buy a card, you pay its price in chips and add it to your playing area. To reserve a card&mdash;in order to make sure you get it, or, why not, your opponents don&#39;t get it&mdash;you place it in front of you face down for later building; this costs you a round, but you also get gold in the form of a joker chip, which you can use as any gem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All of the cards you buy increase your wealth as they give you a permanent gem bonus for later buys; some of the cards also give you prestige points. In order to win the game, you must reach 15 prestige points before your opponents do.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AWARDS &amp; HONORS</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64201/2016-mind-spielepreis-short-game-winner\">2016 MinD-Spielepreis Short Game Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64174/2016-mind-spielepreis-short-game-nominee\">2016 MinD-Spielepreis Short Game Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/27208/2015-origins-awards-best-card-game-nominee\">2015 Origins Awards Best Card Game Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/27638/2015-nederlandse-spellenprijs-best-family-game-win\">2015 Nederlandse Spellenprijs Best Family Game Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/27637/2015-nederlandse-spellenprijs-best-family-game-nom\">2015 Nederlandse Spellenprijs Best Family Game Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/28968/2015-hungarian-board-game-award-nominee\">2015 Hungarian Board Game Award Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64113/2015-hra-roku-winner\">2015 Hra roku Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64316/2015-guldbrikken-best-family-game-winner\">2015 Guldbrikken Best Family Game Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64312/2015-guldbrikken-best-family-game-nominee\">2015 Guldbrikken Best Family Game Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64044/2015-gra-roku-game-year-winner\">2015 Gra Roku Game of the Year Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64046/2015-gra-roku-game-year-nominee\">2015 Gra Roku Game of the Year Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/48615/2015-gioco-dellanno-nominee\">2015 Gioco dell&rsquo;Anno Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/35438/2015-dor-jeu-de-lannee-nominee\">2015 As d&#39;Or - Jeu de l&#39;Ann&eacute;e Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64014/2015-arets-spill-best-family-game-winner\">2015 &Aring;rets Spill Best Family Game Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/63994/2015-arets-spill-best-family-game-nominee\">2015 &Aring;rets Spill Best Family Game Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/55664/2014-vuoden-peli-adult-game-year-nominee\">2014 Vuoden Peli Adult Game of the Year Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/38349/2014-vuoden-peli-adult-game-year\">2014 Vuoden Peli Adult Game of the Year</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/41166/2014-uk-games-expo-best-new-boardgame-winner\">2014 UK Games Expo Best New Boardgame Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/26896/2014-tric-trac-nominee\">2014 Tric Trac Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/26899/2014-tric-trac-de-bronze\">2014 Tric Trac de Bronze</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/25142/2014-spiel-des-jahres-nominee\">2014 Spiel des Jahres Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/27656/2014-meeples-choice-winner\">2014 Meeples&#39; Choice Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/27655/2014-meeples-choice-nominee\">2014 Meeples&#39; Choice Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/35454/2014-lys-grand-public-finalist\">2014 Lys Grand Public Finalist</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/65382/2014-juego-del-ano-recommended\">2014 Juego del A&ntilde;o Recommended</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/65440/2014-jocul-anului-romania-beginners-finalist\">2014 Jocul Anului &icirc;n Rom&acirc;nia Beginners Finalist</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64772/2014-japan-boardgame-prize-voters-selection-winner\">2014 Japan Boardgame Prize Voters&#39; Selection Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/64778/2014-japan-boardgame-prize-u-more-award-nominee\">2014 Japan Boardgame Prize U-more Award Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/26871/2014-golden-geek-board-game-year-winner\">2014 Golden Geek Board Game of the Year Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/26773/2014-golden-geek-board-game-year-nominee\">2014 Golden Geek Board Game of the Year Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/26878/2014-golden-geek-best-family-board-game-winner\">2014 Golden Geek Best Family Board Game Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/26781/2014-golden-geek-best-family-board-game-nominee\">2014 Golden Geek Best Family Board Game Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/26776/2014-golden-geek-best-board-game-artwork-presentat\">2014 Golden Geek Best Board Game Artwork &amp; Presentation Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/61416/2014-board-game-quest-awards-best-family-game-winn\">2014 Board Game Quest Awards Best Family Game Winner</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/61412/2014-board-game-quest-awards-best-family-game-nomi\">2014 Board Game Quest Awards Best Family Game Nominee</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Conclude</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Splendor brings a tactical element, but does not make players think too much or hurt their brains, bringing moments of relaxation and fun with friends. Therefore this is a boardgame that you should not miss.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make the most amazing jewels to become the most famous merchant of all!</p>', 1, '2021-10-02 22:57:48', '2021-10-28 08:07:23'),
(15, 20, 'Raids description', '<p>In more detail, the game lasts four rounds, and at the start of each round tiles are laid out at the various locations on the path that all players must follow. On a turn, a player moves to either an empty spot on the path to claim one of the tiles located there or to an occupied spot. In the latter case, the attacking player must sacrifice a viking, then the defending player must sacrifice two vikings or vacate the space; if they sac two vikings, then the attacker must remove three or leave. Eventually, someone must leave.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can collect runes with an eye toward having lots of the same type or collect goods to sell at the end of the round. You might gather axes to give you better odds against monsters. You can collect more vikings for your crew.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the end of each round, players score majority bonuses depending on the tiles that were revealed before the round started. After four rounds, whoever has the most points wins!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/a97fb8a1-aa15-4ec5-9b5b-f9a6a445663b._CR0,9,992,307_PT0_SX970__.jpg\" /></p>', 0, '2021-10-16 05:06:05', '2023-03-10 01:12:56'),
(16, 4, 'Cosmic Encounter', '<p><strong>This classic game of alien politics returns from the warp once more!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In&nbsp;<em><strong>Cosmic Encounter</strong></em>, each player becomes the leader of one of the dozens of alien races, each with its unique power. On a player&#39;s turn, he or she becomes the offense. The offence encounters another player on a planet by moving a group of his or her ships through the hyperspace gate to that planet. Both sides can invite allies and play cards to try and tip the encounter in their favor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The object of the game is to establish colonies in other players&#39; planetary systems. The winner(s) is the first player(s) to have five colonies on any planet outside his or her home system. These colonies may all be in one system or scattered over multiple systems. The players must use force, cunning, and diplomacy to ensure their victory. And, because alliances are a key part of the game, multiple players can win together!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AWARDS &amp; HONORS</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/8356/2009-golden-geek-best-gamers-board-game-nominee\">2009 Golden Geek Best Gamer&#39;s Board Game Nominee</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamehonor/8420/2009-golden-geek-best-board-game-artworkpresentati\">2009 Golden Geek Best Board Game Artwork/Presentation Nominee</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 1, '2021-07-10 23:57:30', '2021-10-28 08:03:07'),
(17, 3, 'Brain connect', 'Get your brain back on track! In Brain Connect, you need to quickly slide and connect your thoughts in the right order, then be the first to complete the correct action to win. It\'s a race to see who can think and act the fastest! These sliding puzzles have sixteen different starting and stopping points, so creating a clear train of thought is always a new challenge.', 1, '2021-07-10 23:57:30', '2021-10-28 08:03:07'),
(18, 21, 'seven Wonder description', '<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:20,&quot;w&quot;:1465,&quot;h&quot;:40,&quot;abs_x&quot;:319,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1114}\">Each wonder has its own strengths and characteristics. After that, you will go through 3 periods: period 1 with the basics and building the foundation; period 2 with growth and then peaked in period 3. Isn&#39;t it amazing? With the 7 wonders , the strategies of each player are also very important. Brown of self-production, yellow of commercial development, green of science and technology, blue of infrastructure, and even red of military-war.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:73,&quot;w&quot;:1465,&quot;h&quot;:40,&quot;abs_x&quot;:319,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1167}\">Suitable for family and friends gathering. This game trains reasoning and persuasion skills. You&#39;ll have to convince others that you&#39;re &quot;very good and gentle&quot; while quietly winning by planning a strategy in your head. Won by war, economy or scientific and technical development? It&#39;s up to you. Among the world&#39;s top classics of strategy and ancient history, 7 wonders has won a series of major world titles. A Boardgame will definitely be a big omission if you ignore it.</p>', 0, '2021-11-16 10:51:53', '2023-03-10 01:13:03'),
(19, 22, 'Carcassonne description', '<p><img alt=\"carcassonne boardgame\" src=\"https://www.gameosity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/carcassonne-2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Carcassonne is a brick-laying game of the &quot;multi-style&quot; intellectual genre that won the prestigious Spiel de Jahres award in 2001. With many different paths and scoring methods, creating a variety of strategies, corresponding depth. The simple rules of the game make Carcassonne one of the most popular games of modern times.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Content</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The rich and fertile Carcassonne land dreamed of by nomads, is increasingly expanded and developed in a variety of ways by different elements - knight warriors in the castle, farmers on the wings. the fields, the priests in the temple, the thieves in the streets. And only the smartest and most talented will deserve the glory on Carcassonne!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"carcassonne boardgame\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Sx6TaTL.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to play</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each turn you draw a square card and place it in conjunction with other cards available on the table, to expand the land of Carcassonne. You can then choose the right pieces to place on that square card to earn points. You can not place a piece if you want, because if you run out of pieces you will not be placed anymore.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are 4 different ways to score in basic Carcassonne.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each time you score a point, you will take the piece you have placed back, and can use it to place in the next turn. When the cards run out, the game is over. Each player will receive points throughout the game (thanks to the placement of pieces) and points at the end of the game respectively. The person with the most points wins!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prize</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2012 Ludo Award Best Board Game Editor&#39;s Choice Winner<br />\r\n2004 Vuoden Peli Family Game of the Year Winner<br />\r\n2004 Vuoden Peli Family Game of the Year Nominee<br />\r\n2004 Hra roku Nominee<br />\r\n2002 rets Spel Best Family Game Winner<br />\r\n2001 Spiel des Jahres Winner<br />\r\n2001 Spiel des Jahres Nominee<br />\r\n2001 Spiel der Spiele Hit mit Freunden Recommended<br />\r\n2001 Nederlandse Spellenprijs Nominee<br />\r\n2001 International Gamers Awards - General Strategy; Multi-player Nominee<br />\r\n2001 Deutscher Spiele Preis Best Family/Adult Game Winner<br />\r\n2000 Meeples&#39; Choice Award<br />\r\nConclude</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have called yourself a board game fan, like it or not, you must experience Carcassonne once, to understand one of the monuments of this industry. Not too excellent, but no one can deny the popularity of Carcassonne and the addiction it brings to players. You could be the next to prove it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Be the smartest and best to claim glory on Carcassonne!</p>', 0, '2021-11-16 20:17:38', '2023-03-10 01:13:17'),
(20, 23, 'Machi Koro description', '<p>Machi Koro received numerous awards at launch, and has had two major expansions. An indie game based on similar mechanics, Machi Koro Bright Lights, Big City, was launched in 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Machi Koro Review | Board Game Quest\" src=\"https://www.boardgamequest.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Machi-Koro-Header.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to the City of Time. You have just been elected mayor. Congratulation! But the people have a lot of requests for you: jobs, building a park, some cheese factories and even a radio station. A rather difficult task when the city now has only 1 wheat field, a bakery and &hellip; a single dice!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With your trusty dice and a big dream, you&#39;ll have to build Machi Koro into the biggest city in the region. You need to collect money from city building, public works, or&hellip; steal money from your opponent&#39;s coffee shop! But be careful, they can do the same to you!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to play</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Machi Koro is a fast game for 2-4 players. Each player will build their own city to complete all the key constructions before the opponent. On their turn, the player rolls 1 or 2 dice. If the sum of the dice matches the corresponding number on the building, the player gets the house&#39;s capacity; Sometimes even opponents profit from this number. The money in hand will be used by the player to build more new buildings, until one person finishes all the big ones first!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HƯỚNG DẪN LUẬT BOARD GAME MACHI KORO – Thế Giới Board Game\" src=\"https://hstatic.net/936/1000019936/10/2016/1-24/machi-koro-blue-cards.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Prize</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nominees 2015 Spiel des Jahres<br />\r\nNominated 2015 Boardgames Australia Best International Game<br />\r\nNominees 2015 As d&#39;Or - Jeu de l&#39;Ann&eacute;e<br />\r\nShortlist 2014 Lys Grand Public<br />\r\nNominated 2013 Meeples&#39; Choice</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Conclude</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Machi Koro is a light paced fast paced game for you and up to 3 more of your friends. Once you&#39;ve enjoyed Machi Koro, this fun game might make you wonder if the dining table will ever serve another purpose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is said that you cannot build Rome in one day, but Machi Koro will be built&nbsp;in less than 30 minutes!</p>', 0, '2021-11-16 20:30:44', '2023-03-10 01:13:11'),
